text:
Probably the most efficient team and convenient location for a 24hour vault. I find it convenient whenever I need to put some valuable items for clients and need to take it quickly when I am in town. Eric was able to customise the usage to my needs.
Congratulations on your 10th years anniversary.
Vault268 is very professional and facilities are excellent! i would highly recommend ppl to use them. The staff and management are most courteous n helpful.
Very convenient and easy to use facility. Have used for over a year and had no issues. Robotic boxes are super convenient and facility is well secure and safe. Recommended

Jeff has been so helpful in assisting me with my concerns regarding the safe box. He has been patient and addressed my concerns. The company is lucky to have such a person that is commited in providing excellent service to their clients.
The vault 268 gives an excellent service and also very fast in responding to my queries. Will recommend to anyone who needs their service.
